text: Novoyermekeyevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Spartaksky Selsoviet, Yermekeyevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 85 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 14 km from Yermekeyevo, 9 km from Spartak. == References == Category:Rural localities in Yermekeyevsky District
title: Novoyermekeyevo
